4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 eztoc-toggle-hide-by-default' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/bishops-university-application-status\/#How_to_Check_Bishops_University_Application_Status\" title=\"How to Check Bishops University Application Status\">How to Check Bishops University Application Status<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/bishops-university-application-status\/#How_to_accept_the_offer_and_pay_the_Admission_Deposit\" title=\"How to accept the offer and pay the Admission Deposit?\">How to accept the offer and pay the Admission Deposit?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/bishops-university-application-status\/#If_you_are_accepted_at_Bishops_University_What_next\" title=\"If you are accepted at Bishop&#8217;s University, What next\">If you are accepted at Bishop&#8217;s University, What next<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/bishops-university-application-status\/#Accept_Your_Offer\" title=\"Accept Your Offer\">Accept Your Offer<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/bishops-university-application-status\/#Apply_for_Residence_if_applicable\" title=\"Apply for Residence (if applicable)\">Apply for Residence (if applicable)<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/bishops-university-application-status\/#Apply_for_Bishops_University_Financial_Aid_if_applicable\" title=\"Apply for Bishop&#8217;s University Financial Aid (if applicable):\">Apply for Bishop&#8217;s University Financial Aid (if applicable):<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/bishops-university-application-status\/#Register_Bishops_University_Courses\" title=\"Register Bishop&#8217;s University Courses\">Register Bishop&#8217;s University Courses<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/bishops-university-application-status\/#Attend_Orientation\" title=\"Attend Orientation\">Attend Orientation<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p>Bishop\u2019s University Admission is out for all students who applied for admission in the 2024 academic year. Do well to check your application status on https:\/\/<a href=\"https:\/\/www.ubishop.ca\/\" class=\"broken_link\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/www.ubishop.ca\/<\/a><a href=\"http:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">.<\/a>ca to enable you know the required information needed to avoid forfeiting admission.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-check-bishops-university-application-status\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_Check_Bishops_University_Application_Status\"><\/span><strong>How to Check Bishops University Application Status<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<div class=\"group w-full text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 border-b border-black\/10 dark:border-gray-900\/50 dark:bg-gray-800\">\n<div class=\"text-base gap-4 md:gap-6 md:max-w-2xl lg:max-w-xl xl:max-w-3xl p-4 md:py-6 flex lg:px-0 m-auto\">\n<div class=\"relative flex w-[calc(100%-50px)] flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3 lg:w-[calc(100%-115px)]\">\n<div class=\"flex flex-grow flex-col gap-3\">\n<div class=\"min-h-[20px] flex flex-col items-start gap-4 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words\">To access your Bishop&#8217;s University application status, you can follow these steps:<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"group w-full text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 border-b border-black\/10 dark:border-gray-900\/50 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-[#444654]\">\n<div class=\"text-base gap-4 md:gap-6 md:max-w-2xl lg:max-w-xl xl:max-w-3xl p-4 md:py-6 flex lg:px-0 m-auto\">\n<div class=\"relative flex w-[calc(100%-50px)] flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3 lg:w-[calc(100%-115px)]\">\n<div class=\"flex flex-grow flex-col gap-3\">\n<div class=\"min-h-[20px] flex flex-col items-start gap-4 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words\">\n<div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert light\">\n<ol>\n<li>Go to the Bishop&#8217;s University website at <a href=\"http:\/\/www.ubishops.ca\/\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">www.ubishops.ca<\/a>.<\/li>\n<li>Click on the &#8220;Apply&#8221; button at the top right corner of the homepage.<\/li>\n<li>Select &#8220;Check your application status&#8221; from the drop-down menu.<\/li>\n<li>Log in to your application account using the username and password you created when you submitted your application.<\/li>\n<li>Once you are logged in, you should be able to view the current status of your application, including any missing documents or requirements.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-accept-the-offer-and-pay-the-admission-deposit\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_accept_the_offer_and_pay_the_Admission_Deposit\"><\/span><strong>How to accept the offer and pay the Admission Deposit?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Using <strong>www.ubishop.ca<\/strong>. To accept your offer of admission and pay the affirmation deposit where relevant.<\/li>\n<li>click <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/bishops-university-fees\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a><\/strong> to see fees directives for payment<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>The next step is to enroll online; an exact date will be issued to you by the university.<\/p>\n<p>Your account will help you track all things you need to know before and after being admitted.<\/p>\n<p><strong><em>And now you know how to check your application status by checking your student\u2019s account we hope this information was helpful kindly drop your comment in the comment box as we look toward your expectations.<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><em><strong>See also&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;<span class=\"jp-relatedposts-post-title\"><a class=\"jp-relatedposts-post-a\" title=\"Bishop\u2019s University Scholarship 2024\" href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/bishops-university-scholarship\/?relatedposts_hit=1&amp;relatedposts_origin=721&amp;relatedposts_position=0\" data-origin=\"721\" data-position=\"0\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Bishop\u2019s University Scholarship 2024<\/a><\/span><\/strong><\/em><\/p>\n<div class=\"group w-full text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 border-b border-black\/10 dark:border-gray-900\/50 dark:bg-gray-800\">\n<div class=\"text-base gap-4 md:gap-6 md:max-w-2xl lg:max-w-xl xl:max-w-3xl p-4 md:py-6 flex lg:px-0 m-auto\">\n<div class=\"relative flex w-[calc(100%-50px)] flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3 lg:w-[calc(100%-115px)]\">\n<div class=\"flex flex-grow flex-col gap-3\">\n<h2 id=\"if-you-are-accepted-at-bishops-university-what-next\" class=\"min-h-[20px] flex flex-col items-start gap-4 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"If_you_are_accepted_at_Bishops_University_What_next\"><\/span>If you are accepted at Bishop&#8217;s University, What next<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"flex justify-between lg:block\">Congratulations on being accepted to Bishop&#8217;s University! Here are the next steps you should take:<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"group w-full text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 border-b border-black\/10 dark:border-gray-900\/50 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-[#444654]\">\n<div class=\"text-base gap-4 md:gap-6 md:max-w-2xl lg:max-w-xl xl:max-w-3xl p-4 md:py-6 flex lg:px-0 m-auto\">\n<div class=\"relative flex w-[calc(100%-50px)] flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3 lg:w-[calc(100%-115px)]\">\n<div class=\"flex flex-grow flex-col gap-3\">\n<div class=\"min-h-[20px] flex flex-col items-start gap-4 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words\">\n<div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert light\">\n<h3 id=\"accept-your-offer\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Accept_Your_Offer\"><\/span>Accept Your Offer<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Log in to your Bishop&#8217;s University application account to officially accept your offer of admission. You may also need to submit an acceptance deposit to secure your spot.<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"apply-for-residence-if-applicable\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Apply_for_Residence_if_applicable\"><\/span>Apply for Residence (if applicable)<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>If you plan to live on campus, you will need to apply for residence separately. You can do this through the Bishop&#8217;s University Residence Portal.<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"apply-for-bishops-university-financial-aid-if-applicable\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Apply_for_Bishops_University_Financial_Aid_if_applicable\"><\/span>Apply for Bishop&#8217;s University Financial Aid (if applicable):<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>If you need financial assistance to pay for tuition, you can apply for scholarships, bursaries, and student loans through the Bishop&#8217;s University Financial Aid and Awards Office.<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"register-bishops-university-courses\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Register_Bishops_University_Courses\"><\/span>Register Bishop&#8217;s University Courses<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Before you can register for courses, you will need to activate your Bishop&#8217;s University email account and create your student profile. Once you have done that, you can register for courses through the myBU portal.<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"attend-orientation\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Attend_Orientation\"><\/span>Attend Orientation<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Bishop&#8217;s University offers an orientation program for new students to help you get acclimated to campus life, meet other students, and learn about the university&#8217;s resources and services.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Bishops University Application Status &#8211; How to Check Bishops Application Status, How to accept the Offer and pay&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":13042,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[448],"tags":[485],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15691"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=15691"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15691\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":20219,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15691\/revisions\/20219"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/13042"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=15691"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?po